For the relative paths to work, folders 'data' and 'models' should be in the level above the directory of this project. e.g. '../data/filename'

The train, dev and test data can be downloaded from https://github.com/UniversalPropositions/UP-1.0/tree/master/UP_English-EWT

Each assignement has a final ready to use function, to which one may pass a sentence in tokenized in strings, the binary position of the target verb in said sentence,
and the model adn vectorizer or tokenizer.




